Mystery, Sci-fi film from 2018, titled A Breath&nbsp;
Away. Spoilers ahead! Watch out and take care.&nbsp;

00:00:10.480 --> 00:00:14.720
The movie starts with a dream: it shows an&nbsp;
ultrasound, then a newborn baby and a girl&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:14.720 --> 00:00:19.200
running on an open field. We suddenly cut to&nbsp;
our protagonist, Mathieu, who is waking up from&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:23.760
this dream in a plan currently in the process of&nbsp;
landing in France. On his way out of the airport,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:28.240
he calls his twelve-year-old daughter, Sarah, to&nbsp;
check on her and tell her he'll be there soon.&nbsp;

