After a quick drive through the highway, he&nbsp;
arrives at his apartment, where he gets a call&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:32.080 --> 00:00:36.720
from Sarah through the walkie-talkie. She asks&nbsp;
him to come over to her mom's place. After taking&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:36.720 --> 00:00:40.880
a box out of his bag, he leaves his apartment and&nbsp;
crosses the street to enter a different building&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:40.880 --> 00:00:45.600
as one of the neighbors, Mr. Belkacem, who is&nbsp;
also making his way inside. Mathieu helps him&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:45.600 --> 00:00:50.240
with his oxygen tank then quickly goes upstairs&nbsp;
and knocks on her wife Anna's door. She welcomes&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:50.240 --> 00:00:54.160
him with a kiss and tells him she's in the middle&nbsp;
of teaching an online class, so while waiting,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:54.160 --> 00:00:58.960
Mathieu goes to see his daughter in another room.&nbsp;
Sarah is living in a hermetically sealed capsule&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:58.960 --> 00:01:03.360
that filters her air because she has a total&nbsp;
allergy auto-immune syndrome. After saying hi to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:03.360 --> 00:01:08.080
her and asking her about her crush, he gives her&nbsp;
the box he's brought as a gift. Sarah opens it and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:12.400
finds natural scents from Canada, which is weird&nbsp;
because her dad supposedly went to Marseille:&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:16.560
Mathieu asks her to check under the bottles,&nbsp;
and when she does, she finds an SD card that&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:21.200
she quickly moves to put in her virtual reality&nbsp;
set. Mathieu recorded the Rocky Mountains for her.&nbsp;

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:26.240
We next cut to Anna, who is finishing her&nbsp;
online class. Mathieu comes to talk to her&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:01:26.240 --> 00:01:30.080
then - he tells her he didn't go to Marseille&nbsp;
for an interview, he went to Canada because a&nbsp;&nbsp;

