when he finds the oxygen tank a moment later.&nbsp;
He puts the mask on and covers the holes with&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:41.040 --> 00:05:45.360
the tape and when hears his wife calling out, he&nbsp;
peeks out the window to tell her he's fine. While&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:45.360 --> 00:05:49.440
grabbing a bag to put the tank in and carry it on&nbsp;
his back, he hears some noises coming from another&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:49.440 --> 00:05:54.720
room: when he opens it, a puppy runs out, and&nbsp;
Mathieu notices the body of the dog parent inside.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:54.720 --> 00:05:59.840
He leaves the apartment and goes to see Sarah, who&nbsp;
is scared. Mathieu leaves her food, a flashlight&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:59.840 --> 00:06:03.600
and some batteries for the walkie-talkie&nbsp;
before changing the battery of the capsule.&nbsp;&nbsp;

