After giving Mathieu one of his masks,&nbsp;
the soldier tries to take him with him,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:38.640 --> 00:06:43.600
but Mathieu turns down the offer, explaining his&nbsp;
family situation and asking for one extra mask.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:48.080
The soldier gives it to him before leaving.
