00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:47.280
an open field again, which is interrupted when&nbsp;
Mathieu wakes up in the morning. He finds Anna&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:47.280 --> 00:07:51.200
working on the radio with tools she's brought&nbsp;
from her place and she finally manages to fix it,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:51.200 --> 00:07:55.520
but all the channels are transmitting the same&nbsp;
emergency recording on repeat. Suddenly they hear&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:55.520 --> 00:07:59.840
an exploding noise from outside, so Mathieu and&nbsp;
Anna go out to the roof to see what's going on:&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:59.840 --> 00:08:04.320
there's fire on Montmartre, the riots have&nbsp;
started. Once they return to the apartment,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:04.320 --> 00:08:07.680
Anna says they should go to stay at Charlotte's&nbsp;
because they live on a hill and Sarah could&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:12.080
share her friend's capsule. Lucien thinks Sarah&nbsp;
shouldn't leave her capsule, but Mathieu explains&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:12.080 --> 00:08:16.400
there are special suits they can use to move her,&nbsp;
