00:08:16.400 --> 00:08:20.400
says it's easy to get lost to reach that place&nbsp;
so she should go because she's been there before,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:20.400 --> 00:08:25.040
Mathieu decides to go with her to protect her.
