00:08:25.040 --> 00:08:29.600
plan and that they left the walkie-talkie with&nbsp;
Lucien in case she need anything. Sarah asks them&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:29.600 --> 00:08:35.200
to check on NoÃ©, who lives nearby. A moment later,&nbsp;
Mathieu and Anna are out on the streets, and they&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:35.200 --> 00:08:40.080
quickly reach NoÃ©'s building. They aren't able to&nbsp;
make it inside though, because an angry dog shows&nbsp;&nbsp;

