up and starts chasing them. They start running&nbsp;
away and after some blocks, accidentally get&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:49.280
separated while dodging cars. Anna's calls for his&nbsp;
husband distract Mathieu, who ends up falling into&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:49.280 --> 00:08:54.480
the Seine river. Anna manages to hide behind a car&nbsp;
at first, but when she accidentally makes a noise,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:54.480 --> 00:08:59.440
the dog finds her again and resumes the chase.&nbsp;
