taken from a random body. He also notices there's&nbsp;
a hazmat suit inside a fallen van. Back to Anna,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:25.760 --> 00:09:30.240
she's finally reached the lab and when she's about&nbsp;
to enter, she finds Mathieu running toward her.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:35.360
After checking on each other, they get inside.&nbsp;
Meanwhile, Sarah is playing battleship with Lucien&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:40.640
through the walkie-talkie, and Lucien is cheating.
