00:09:40.640 --> 00:09:44.480
and a small fire in one of the rooms, but they&nbsp;
keep going until they find a suitcase with the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:44.480 --> 00:09:49.520
suit they need. On their way out, they pass by&nbsp;
the room on fire again but this time it explodes,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:49.520 --> 00:09:53.920
pushing them back against the wall.&nbsp;
