She manages to hold her breath long&nbsp;
enough to return to Lucien's place,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:54.800 --> 00:10:59.040
where she discovers the explosion has damaged&nbsp;
the suitcase and its contents. Meanwhile,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:59.040 --> 00:11:03.760
Mathieu finds some provisions and a rope on one of&nbsp;
the rooftops. After giving the rope a tug to test&nbsp;&nbsp;

