and a trail of blood that takes him to the body&nbsp;
of a cop. Then he enters the building and finds&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:16.880
a little camp that holds an oxygen tank and a&nbsp;
rifle. He takes the tank for himself and when&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:16.880 --> 00:11:21.360
he's about to leave, a different cop shows up that&nbsp;
