Mathieu turns abruptly to dodge him and crashes.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:44.640 --> 00:13:48.640
In the capsule, Sarah is trying to call him on&nbsp;
the walkie-talkie to no avail and she freezes&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:48.640 --> 00:13:52.800
when a mysterious someone enters her room.
On the street, Mathieu is slowly regaining&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:52.800 --> 00:13:56.640
consciousness and notices he has quite a&nbsp;
wound on his head. He retrieves the suit&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:56.640 --> 00:14:00.160
