the building while trying to get in contact with&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:00.160 --> 00:14:04.720
his daughter. He barely manages to take a couple&nbsp;
of steps before he must stop to rest on the floor&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:04.720 --> 00:14:08.560
because the pain is unbearable, but he forces&nbsp;
himself to stand up when he sees two shadows&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:08.560 --> 00:14:13.520
