happy that he takes off his mask for a second&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:22.320 --> 00:14:26.320
so he can kiss Sarah's head while hugging&nbsp;
her again. He tells her she's finally free.&nbsp;

00:14:27.040 --> 00:14:30.960
We cut to the dream one last time, this time&nbsp;
we clearly see it's Sarah the one running on&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:30.960 --> 00:14:35.520
